comments: Finney-Smith (DAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) path following the hand-off and absorbs the contact.

Replay review of the foul called on Pokusevski (OKC) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Pokusevski jumps forward and moves into Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) space and would make contact even if Hardaway Jr. did not extend his leg.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) has his arm around Dort's (OKC) midsection and quickly slides it off as Dort sets the pick.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) brings his off-arm toward Finney-Smith (DAL) and marginal contact occurs as Gilgeous-Alexander naturally releases away.
Finney-Smith (DAL) firms up in his screening position in Maledon's (OKC) path and absorbs the contact.

Pokusevski (OKC) is moving alongside Brunson's (DAL) path and absorbs the body contact when Brunson veers backward during the driving shot attempt. Pokusevski contests the shot attempt and marginal contact occurs with Brunson's arm after the release.
Richardson (DAL) and Dort (OKC) engage and disengage with one another as the pick is set.
Richardson's (DAL) hand is extended outward when marginal contact occurs with Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) right arm after his gather.
Finney-Smith (DAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Dort's (OKC) path and absorbs the contact.
Horford (OKC) initiates contact across Kleber's (DAL) right arm prior to making any contact with the ball during his upward shooting motion.
Dort (OKC) extends slightly as he firms up in his screening position and absorbs the contact made with Finney-Smith (DAL).
Brunson's (DAL) hand is extended forward as marginal contact occurs with Dort's (OKC) right arm at the end of the drive.
Brunson (DAL) firms up in his screening position in Pokusevski's (OKC) path following the hand-off and absorbs the contact.
Maledon (OKC) is moving somewhat laterally as body contact occurs with Richardson (DAL) and Richardson is able to move through the marginal contact to finish at the rim.
Richardson's (DAL) left hand is extended outward when marginal contact occurs with Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) right arm as he changes direction.
Kleber (DAL) extends forward and initiates body contact with Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) that affects his SQBR.
Kleber (DAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) path and absorbs the contact.
Horford (OKC) extends his arm forward and initiates contact with Brunson's (DAL) front/right arm after his gather.
Brunson (DAL) commits a take foul on Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC).
Kleber (DAL) firms up in his screening position in Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) path and absorbs the contact.
Maledon (OKC) cleanly dislodges the ball away from Richardson (DAL) before incidental arm contact occurs.
Finney-Smith (DAL) commits a take foul on Pokusevski (OKC).
Kleber (DAL) establishes himself in a screening position in Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) path and absorbs the contact.
Pokusevski (OKC) cleanly blocks Finney-Smith's (DAL) jump shot attempt.
